Class FlightMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • FlightMap

  • public class FlightMap
extends java.lang.Object

    FlightMap

    The FlightMap class is used to create a map of the flights from an origin. This class also countains a search algorithm that is used to parse through the flights from the origin and output a list of connecting flight paths with the lowest cost.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jordan Ghidossi
